Introduction

MayLiz (메이리즈) is a South Korean girl group under One Music Office and LST Entertainment. They debuted on December 20, 2023 with the digital single "Tonight".

On December 2, 2024, MayLiz introduced a new member, Yena, via their official Instagram. Notably, Chaea was unfollowed by the official Instagram and it was assumed that she had quietly left the group sometime in 2024.
